result.name: 2009-defra-mb0102-2a-ebb-tidal-delta
result.notes: Ebb tidal deltas located within UK Territorial waters. Obtained through reference to the Estuary Guide (www.estuary-guide.net). This dataset is associated with a series of digital maps/spatial information layers that are designed to help identify Marine Conservation Zones (MCZs) in UK waters. (see Project MB0102: 'Accessing and developing the required biophysical datasets and datalayers for Marine Protected Areas network planning and wider marine spatial planning purposes' - Report No.8, Task 2a Mapping of Geological and Geomorphological Features)

extras.value: ["Full resolution GIS layer only for viewing by MB0102 partners with publicly available layers available at 10km resolution."]

Full resolution data layer for use only within the MB0102 contract. Permission required from data originators for use in any other context, or by non MB0102 partners. 10km resolution data layer freely available under Open Government Licence.
Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs (DEFRA) (custodian); Marine Biological Association of the UK (MBA) (originator)
